WEBVTT


00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:04.000
here's The Good Wife's guide to how you can be a good wife to your husband

00:00:04.001 --> 00:00:05.841
No. 1 have dinner ready

00:00:05.842 --> 00:00:07.621
this should come as a no brainer

00:00:07.760 --> 00:00:10.240
The way to a man's heart is always through his stomach

00:00:10.241 --> 00:00:13.321
so make sure you plan ahead the night before

00:00:13.322 --> 00:00:16.281
to ensure that he has a delicious meal when he comes home.

00:00:16.282 --> 00:00:19.481
And make sure it's ready on time when he returns home from work

00:00:19.482 --> 00:00:24.341
okay this ensures that he knows that you're thinking about him and his needs

00:00:24.520 --> 00:00:27.600
he's at work trying to provide for you and your family

00:00:27.601 --> 00:00:29.401
so make sure when he gets home

00:00:29.402 --> 00:00:31.721
he has a warm meal ready for him

00:00:31.722 --> 00:00:35.641
to relieve his stress and make him fall in love with you all over again

00:00:35.642 --> 00:00:37.361
No. 2 you prepare yourself

00:00:37.362 --> 00:00:41.001
 make sure you take a couple minutes to yourself before he gets home

00:00:41.002 --> 00:00:42.041
and freshen up

00:00:42.042 --> 00:00:43.501
maybe take shower

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:45.080
Run a brush through your hair,

00:00:45.081 --> 00:00:46.241
touch up your makeup,

00:00:46.242 --> 00:00:49.221
you know you, want to feel fresh for his right

00:00:49.600 --> 00:00:51.440
Not only that if you look good

00:00:51.441 --> 00:00:52.201
you feel good

00:00:52.202 --> 00:00:53.881
so this doesn't just help him

00:00:53.882 --> 00:00:55.201
this helps you out too

00:00:55.202 --> 00:00:56.521
remember he's been at work

00:00:56.522 --> 00:00:59.521
he's been around office people or drabby people

00:00:59.522 --> 00:01:00.841
you don't wanna be one of them

00:01:00.842 --> 00:01:03.901
you want to be his breath of fresh air when he gets home

00:01:04.080 --> 00:01:07.000
No. 3 be happy and interesting for him

00:01:07.001 --> 00:01:08.481
His boring day might need a lift

00:01:08.482 --> 00:01:12.441
so one of your duties is to provide him happiness and peace

00:01:12.442 --> 00:01:14.661
4 tidy up the house

00:01:14.760 --> 00:01:17.080
throw away any clutter before he gets home

00:01:17.081 --> 00:01:19.121
he doesn't wanna come home after work

00:01:19.122 --> 00:01:21.441
and you're chilling on the couch with a bag of chips,

00:01:21.442 --> 00:01:22.821
and the house is chaos

00:01:22.840 --> 00:01:25.880
instead tidy up the main parts of the house

00:01:25.881 --> 00:01:28.401
you know wipe off the crumbs off the counter

00:01:28.402 --> 00:01:31.201
this allows him to relax when he gets off work

00:01:31.202 --> 00:01:33.941
No. 5 minimize noise in the house

00:01:34.160 --> 00:01:37.680
okay you want your house to be calming environment when he gets off work

00:01:37.681 --> 00:01:40.301
so make sure you do the laundry

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:41.360
do the vacuuming

00:01:41.361 --> 00:01:42.701
all before he gets home

00:01:42.920 --> 00:01:46.280
and encourage the children to have some quiet time

00:01:46.281 --> 00:01:49.341
maybe put on a movie or put them down for a nap

00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:51.560
When he gets home from a stressful day

00:01:51.561 --> 00:01:54.321
he needs to relax and unwind

00:01:54.322 --> 00:01:57.100
Reflect on this guide for how you can be a good wife to your partner
